    Contains a 10 character string that is guaranteed to be a semantically valid blog IntegerDatum.

    BlogIDs
    The main responsibility of this singleton class is to issue a new blog object IntegerDatum when one is needed.
    BlogObject
    Represents an object stored on the blog, which could be metadata, static (including template generated) content, or content generated by code.
    BlogObjectContent
    Encapsulates the notion of content to be written to an HTTP response.
